Title   : Samvat 2082 Outlook: BFSI, hospitals, travel in focus, says Kotak’s Chouhan 
Source  : www.thehindubusinessline.com
Published: 2025-10-18T10:43:39
Fetched : 2025-10-18T17:47:38.612192
URL     : https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/multimedia/audio/samvat-2082-outlook-bfsi-hospitals-travel-in-focus-says-kotaks-chouhan/article70178886.ece
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Listen. Samvat 2082 Outlook: BFSI, hospitals, travel in focus, says Kotak’s Chouhan Shrikant Chouhan of Kotak Securities expects 7.9% earnings growth in FY26, with BFSI, hospitals, and travel sectors poised to lead a recovery supported by policy tailwinds. By Anupama Ghosh Shakthi H Updated - October 18, 2025  at 04:46 PM. × Share WhatsApp X Facebook LinkedIn Messenger Reddit Mail https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/multimedia/audio/samvat-2082-outlook-bfsi-hospitals-travel-in-focus-says-kotaks-chouhan/article70178886.ece Copy In this episode of the businessline Podcast, Anupama Ghosh speaks to Shrikant Chouhan, Head of Equity Research at Kotak Securities, who shares his views on the market outlook, earnings trends, sectoral opportunities, and the FII flow trajectory as India steps into a year of policy tailwinds and potential growth revival. From why BFSI and hospital stocks could lead the rally to how investors should position portfolios for growth and recovery — this episode offers a crisp, data-backed view on navigating the year ahead. (Host: Anupama Ghosh , Producer: Shakthi H ) Comments Published on  October 18, 2025 READ MORE THIS AD SUPPORTS OUR JOURNALISM. SUBSCRIBE FOR MINIMAL ADS. THIS AD SUPPORTS OUR JOURNALISM. SUBSCRIBE FOR MINIMAL ADS. THIS AD SUPPORTS OUR JOURNALISM. SUBSCRIBE FOR MINIMAL ADS.

