Title   : Connplex Cinemas opens in Maharashtra, Odisha
Source  : www.thehindubusinessline.com
Published: 2025-10-17T16:36:39
Fetched : 2025-10-18T17:50:57.670577
URL     : https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/companies/connplex-cinemas-opens-in-maharashtra-odisha/article70176034.ece
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Connplex Cinemas, one of India’s fastest-growing entertainment companies, has launched operations in two new properties in Maharashtra and Odisha.
The company has added a 3-screen cinema with 208 seats in Jajpur, Odisha, and a 2-screen cinema with 268 seats in Sangamner, Maharashtra.
With these additions, Connplex’s operational footprint now stands at 88 screens across 33 properties in 25 cities and 9 states, offering a total of 7,307 ultra-comfort seats nationwide.
The latest expansion follows a strong streak of openings in Hyderabad, Bharuch, Anand and Gurugram, further strengthening the company’s presence across key growth markets.
Both properties are equipped with advanced Dolby 7.1 surround sound systems, 2K and 3D Screen, and luxury recliner seating, designed to deliver an immersive and comfortable viewing experience.
The launches reflect Connplex’s focused strategy of building a premium yet affordable cinema network across tier-II and -III cities as well as select metro locations.
Rahul Kamleshbhai Dhyani, Joint Managing Director of Connplex Cinemas, said with the latest openings in Odisha and Maharashtra the company has started its nationwide growth journey.
Published on October 17, 2025

